The paper deals with the issue of false discoveries in scientific studies and proposes a system for ensuring the application of false discovery control procedures in hypothesis testing. This involves the use of cryptographic techniques and secure computation protocols, which are typically studied in the areas of computer security (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), machine learning (cs.LG), and cryptography (cs.CY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
